<br>
This thing has a lot of leg left in it. But .... For this to fade something will have to takes its place. So far there is no game out there that even competes. DOAC was the closest and about 80% that ran to that thinkin it was the EQ killa are back in EQ. So talk about how the content is lame or unfinished or bugged or the expansion suck BLAH BLAH BLAH BLAH. But know they are still getting your 8.95 to 10 dollars a month.<br>
<br>
I am not an EQ defender although I like the game and If something replaces it tomorrow so be it. But the posters that use the same arguements of EQ sucks while they still spend their money is annoying. Gotta love the idiot hypocrite. <br>
